    {
      "type": "html",
      "id": "6bcd85b7a13e91a1",
      "text": "<blockquote>\n”was not restricted to technology in a narrow sense ... but referred to all kinds of rationally designed institutions like schools and bureaucracies.\"\n(Illich,1973). "
    },
